"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gathered, together"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a thing:"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "drew and joined,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "adjoined,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "one thing to another. This is the primary signification. (L.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasajati", "text_ar": "نَسَجَتِ"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 2788}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~iyHu Alwaraqa wAlha$iyma", "text_ar": "الرِّيحُ الوَرَقَ والهَشِيمَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind gathered together the leaves and the dry fragments of plants."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "Hence, accord. to some,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasaja Alv~awoba", "text_ar": "نَسَجَ الثَّوْبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", because the weaver adjoins the warp to the woof. (TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasajati", "text_ar": "نَسَجَتِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~iyHu Alt~uraAba", "text_ar": "الرِّيحُ التُّرَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind drew the dust together."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasajati Alr~iyHu AlmaA='a", "text_ar": "نَسَجَتِ الرِّيحُ المَا=ءَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~amola", "text_ar": "الرَّمْلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alt~uraAba", "text_ar": "التُّرَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rasoma Ald~aAri", "text_ar": "رَسْمَ الدَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind made rippling lines, in cross directions, upon the water, and the sand, and the dust, and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with dust"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon the traces of the dwelling."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) [And so]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TaraAy^iqu kaA@loHubuki", "text_ar": "طَرَايِقُ كَا@لْحُبُكِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_inotasajato", "text_ar": "اـِنْتَسَجَتْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Rippling lines were made, in cross directions,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by the wind, upon the water, (S, * A,) and the sand, and the dust, and the traces of the dwelling. (A.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasajati", "text_ar": "نَسَجَتِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~iyHu Alr~aboEa", "text_ar": "الرِّيحُ الرَّبْعَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind, blowing in cross directions, obliterated the traces of the place where persons had alighted,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K,) [by covering it with dust or sand in such a manner as that it might be likened to a web]. ―         -b6-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasaja", "text_ar": "نَسَجَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a spider)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wove,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "spun,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "its web. (A.) ―         -b7-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasaja Alv~awoba", "text_ar": "نَسَجَ الثَّوْبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasojN", "text_ar": "نَسْجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He wove the piece of cloth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the garment."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA, &c.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasaja sayorFA", "text_ar": "نَسَجَ سَيْرًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He plaited a thong."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA, in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "tex